{"html": [{"t": "<div><div class=\"p\">MODIFICA DECRETO No. 3.245, DE 1982</div><br><div class=\"p\">N&#xFA;m. 602.- Santiago 10 de Julio de 1990.- Visto: Lo dispuesto en el art&#xED;culo 16 de la Ley No. 18.956, de 1990, y en los art&#xED;culos 32 No. 8 y 35 de la Constituci&#xF3;n Pol&#xED;tica de la Rep&#xFA;blica de Chile,</div><br><div class=\"p\">Decreto:</div><br></div>", "i": 7225294}, {"t": "<div><div class=\"p\">Art&#xED;culo &#xFA;nico.- Modif&#xED;case el Decreto Supremo de Educaci&#xF3;n No. 3245, de 1982, en el sentido de sustituir las menciones de su art&#xED;culo 1&#xB0; respecto de la X Regi&#xF3;n en la forma que se indica a continuaci&#xF3;n:</div><br><br><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  Direcci&#xF3;n</div><div class=\"p\">Regi&#xF3;n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  Provincial&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  Provincias&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  Comunas</div><br><div class=\"p\">10&#xAA;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Llanquihue&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  Llanquihue&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  Puerto Montt</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  Puerto Varas</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  Cocham&#xF3;</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  Maull&#xED;n</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  Los Muermos</div><div clas